{"tid":2388420,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企成日有磨牙聲","createTime":"2021-01-31T06:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T07:59:10.000Z","uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f26fb5589366218f45162cdf66e5754e509f7bd","tid":2388420,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:16:44.000Z","msg":"已經好多年<br />\n無論朝頭早同夜晚 全屋間唔中都會有D磨牙聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD聲好有規律 每次都係4-5秒<br />\n一開始由低音磨到變中低音再變返低音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網完全搵唔到其他人有呢個問題<br />\n應該唔關老鼠事? 屋企都有壁虎 但係壁虎應該唔係咁叫的?<br />\n有無人知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7591dc30fe63435dea67e13a3758c851052591","tid":2388420,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:19:44.000Z","msg":"即係點?"},{"pid":"066dfea24596a2ed37833f14c3fc4f0bf89b5b68","tid":2388420,"uid":180401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"搬"},{"pid":"4843bb3a8bc7a5b385fac9017118e3b3b6e31175","tid":2388420,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe7591dc30fe63435dea67e13a3758c851052591","tid":2388420,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:19:44.000Z","msg":"即係點?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:50:24.000Z","msg":"應該係唔知咩蟲係到叫緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c03263ae45ca065433479eb16340d62b670b6f","tid":2388420,"uid":59522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-3